      Ethcon Korea


      Supporting the open-source movement as a non profit Ethereum developer conference, Ethcon Korea have started its journey since 2019. We as organizers believe that Ethereum is more than just a technical solution - it is a community. 


      Our mission is to empower local communities by bridging the gap between Korea and the world through the promotion of decentralized protocols, tools, and culture. Our commitment to fostering innovation and community continues with this Hackathon and conference, and we look forward to supporting the growth of the Ethereum ecosystem here.

      Empowerment in Action


      Your Ethcon ticket does more than grant access; it fuels innovation. While the main prizes are still determined by our panel of judges, this year we're experimenting with an exciting addition. 


      On the final day, September 3, you'll have a unique opportunity to directly influence which projects receive a portion of the QF prize pool.Be part of this process and feel the direct impact of your vote on the projects and our community. To learn more about QF, click here
